* Behavioral analysis

---

## 23.2 Assessment Objectives

The assessment shall determine whether:

* Prevention features are appropriately enabled.
* Detection signatures are current.
* Threat policies align with organizational risk.
* High-risk traffic receives enhanced inspection.
