# 24. Operational Decision Gates

To maintain consistency and quality, each major assessment stage shall conclude with a formal decision gate.

| Decision Gate | Validation Requirement         | Outcome                         |
| ------------- | ------------------------------ | ------------------------------- |
| DG-01         | Information gathering complete | Proceed to technical assessment |
| DG-02         | Architecture validated         | Proceed to control assessment   |
| DG-03         | Technical reviews complete     | Proceed to evidence validation  |
| DG-04         | Evidence verified              | Proceed to risk evaluation      |
| DG-05         | Risk analysis approved         | Proceed to reporting            |

Assessment activities shall not progress beyond a decision gate until mandatory validation criteria have been satisfied.

