# 52. AI-Ready Assessment Architecture

EFSAF is designed to support AI-assisted assessment workflows while maintaining human oversight.

AI capabilities may assist with:

* Configuration parsing
* Policy analysis
* Rule optimization
* Duplicate rule detection
* Risk correlation
* Compliance mapping
* Evidence indexing
* Report drafting
* Recommendation generation
* Security scoring support

AI-generated outputs shall always be reviewed and approved by qualified assessors before inclusion in official deliverables.

---

## 52.1 AI Governance Principles

Organizations using AI within EFSAF shall ensure:

* Human accountability
* Transparency of AI usage
* Validation of AI-generated outputs
* Protection of sensitive information
* Secure handling of assessment data
* Auditability of AI-assisted decisions
* Compliance with applicable legal and organizational policies

AI shall augment, not replace, professional judgment.

