# 57. Summary

EFSAF-METH-001 establishes the official operational methodology for conducting enterprise firewall security assessments under the Enterprise Firewall Security Assessment Framework.

By integrating governance, planning, technical execution, evidence management, risk evaluation, compliance validation, scoring, reporting, quality assurance, and continuous improvement into a single standardized methodology, EFSAF enables organizations to deliver **consistent, repeatable, auditable, and enterprise-grade firewall assessments** across diverse technologies and environments.

This methodology serves as the operational backbone of EFSAF v1.1 and is fully aligned with:

